cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with modeling visual attributes, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The approach proposed by the authors involves learning a semantic embedding and regularizers, which are techniques commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also validates the approach on challenging datasets, which is a common practice in multimedia (cs.MM).
